            <div type="translation" xml:lang="en" resp="#AA">
                <p>To the great and invincible imperator Caesar Aurelius Antoninus Pius Felix Augustus, the colony of Minturnae devotes this to his divine power and majesty.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>This statue base to Elagabalus suffered erasure of his name, after his damnatio.</p> <!-- -->
